# Basic HTML Webpage

A simple webpage demonstrating fundamental HTML elements.

## 📌 Features

- Heading elements
- Hyperlink integration
- Image embedding
- Basic page structure

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in any web browser.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- HTML page structure
- Linking external websites
- Displaying images
- Understanding core HTML tags

